HEADWORD: activated
<hw>activated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Sewage
treatment)</fld> <def>treated with aeration and bacteria to aid
decomposition; -- of sewage</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>made reactive or more reactive;
